title: Mark Carney Meets ‘Heated Rivalry’ Star Hudson Williams
summary_full: Only one thing could make the TV show and cultural phenomenon “Heated Rivalry” more Canadian: pairing one of its stars, Hudson Williams, with Prime Minister Mark Carney in the nation’s capital.
